WEBVTT

00:08:28.100 --> 00:08:30.548
kuliko kukubali kwamba hautowajua.

00:08:31.937 --> 00:08:36.409
Kila asubuhi Japan, ua likiwaka kwenye
nyumba yetu ndogo,

00:08:36.433 --> 00:08:40.791
inanichukua maumivu mengi 
kutokuangalia utabiri wa hali ya hewa,

00:08:40.815 --> 00:08:42.453
sababu nikiangalia,

00:08:42.477 --> 00:08:45.740
akili yangu itajawa na mawazo,
na itasumbuka

00:08:45.764 --> 00:08:48.278
hata kama siku ikiwa angavu.

00:08:50.160 --> 00:08:54.353
Nimekuwa mwandishi kwa miaka 34 sasa.

00:08:54.816 --> 00:08:57.696
Na kitu kimoja ambacho nimejifunza

00:08:57.720 --> 00:09:01.256
ni kua mabadiliko huja pale
nisipoyapangilia,